. heck, give us a aa ability that each point improves the ration of mana transfer, up to a 2:1 transferred to cost... we would be uber mana batteries, and would fulfill our verant designed purpose.</P><P>so what if my dots stack with another necros or another shaman/druid dots... if 3 necros all drop funeral pyre it should damage the mob funeral pyre X 3.... after all, when do wizzies/mages see that their nuke wont stack because another wizzy just cast the same spell or one that uses the same checks for resistances... our funeral pyre does about 2khp per minute... wizzies can do that with one spell that crits in 4 secs... 10 secs with recast, thats close to 20k damage, over a minute. we dont compare, fine... but let our dots stack so more than just one necro is allowed to damage on raids, and the others all get to feed mana...</P><P>/setgroupfeign = true (now, if necro casts group fd, everyone in group gets to fd if they trust necro to save em... our version of an evac... checks for resists and fails, and being cast on for each person, so not as good as evac, but still has a chance at saving group)</P><P></P><P><BR> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
